      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken such good care of it, and it's been garage-kept since day one. Not a single scratch or dent anywhere \u2013 it\u2019s absolutely flawless. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
