    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, and it shows. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel is original and perfectly aligned. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats are firm and free of any bolster wear or creasing, and it still carries that distinct new-car aroma. All electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function with precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is flawless. It comes with a complete, documented service history from the original dealership, showing preventative maintenance performed well ahead of schedule. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its low-mileage life on paved roads only. This is an impeccable example for a discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
